## ros_dynamixel_controller


# USB Latency Setup
For high frequency communication, there needs to be a lower latency_timer. Note this eats away at the CPU.
```
sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/set-usb-latency.service


[Unit]
Description=Set USB serial latency timer
After=syslog.target

[Service]
Type=oneshot
ExecStart=/bin/bash -c 'echo 1 > /sys/bus/usb-serial/devices/ttyUSB0/latency_timer'

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target


sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable set-usb-latency.service
```